    <title>VIM - common used cmd!</title>
    <url>/2022/10/14/VIM-common-used-cmd/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9f/Vimlogo.svg" alt="" style="width:50%" />  

<h2 id="case-1-to-delete-and-add-same-content-in-multi-lines"><a href="#case-1-to-delete-and-add-same-content-in-multi-lines" class="headerlink" title="case 1 - to delete and add same content in multi lines"></a>case 1 - to delete and add same content in multi lines</h2><p>before change</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">item1</span><br><span class="line">item2</span><br><span class="line">item3</span><br><span class="line">item4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="add"><a href="#add" class="headerlink" title="add"></a>add</h3><ol>
<li>move the cursor at the first line first character</li>
<li>ctrl + v and enter visual block mode</li>
<li>use motion key or run “3gg” to select all </li>
<li>input I (upper case) to enter Edit mode</li>
<li>input the content you want to insert</li>
<li>ESC and wait for a moment</li>
</ol>
<p>after change</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">my_item1</span><br><span class="line">my_item2</span><br><span class="line">my_item3</span><br><span class="line">my_item4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="delete"><a href="#delete" class="headerlink" title="delete"></a>delete</h3><ol>
<li>move the cursor at the first line first character</li>
<li>ctrl + v and enter visual block mode</li>
<li>use motion key or run “3j3l” to select what you want to delete </li>
<li>enter “d” to delete<br>tip: after delete, we could still use ‘p’ to paste the deleted sentence which means ‘delete’ is like ‘cut’.</li>
</ol>
<hr />
<p style="text-align: center">
<font face='comic'> 
Copyright &copy; 2022-<script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear())</script> Emily Peng All Rights Reserved
</font>
</p>
]]></content>
