    <title>To generate random numbers in C</title>
    <url>/2022/10/18/To-generate-random-numbers-in-C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>For randomly gerenating number, we could use &lt;stdlib.h&gt; header file in order to leverage the rand function. Each time rand() is called, it would generate a totally random number. However, it would generate the same value if the environment&#x2F;program kept unchanging. Thus here we introduce another function srand() which is used to create a seed value. The input parameter could set as time since time changes and makes sure the seed various.</p>
<p>To generate floating number, we could type cast value to (float)rand();</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;time.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#define MAX_CYCLE (50)</span><br><span class="line">#define MAX_NUM (20)</span><br><span class="line">#define MIN_NUM (10)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    int rand_num, count = 0;</span><br><span class="line">    for (count = 0; count &lt; MAX_CYCLE; count++)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">       if (0 == count%5)</span><br><span class="line">       &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            srand(time(0));     // The seed value is kept on changing</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     printf(&quot;The randomly generated number is between (%d, %d)&quot;, MIN_NUM, MAX_NUM);</span><br><span class="line">     rand_num = rand()%(MAX_NUM - MIN_NUM) + MIN_NUM;</span><br><span class="line">     printf(&quot;%d\n&quot;, rand_num);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr />
<p style="text-align: center">
<font face='comic'> 
Copyright &copy; 2022-<script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear())</script> Emily Peng All Rights Reserved
</font>
</p>
]]></content>
