    <title>how to write your motivation letter?</title>
    <url>/2022/12/22/how-to-write-your-motivation-letter/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<ol>
<li><p>For different job, do enough research and write different motivation letter. Some people like to write only one general letter and use it for all applications which is awful.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Be sincere, write down your own story. Do not be boastful or unrealistic. Do not care much about using complicated sentences. </p>
</li>
<li><p>Usually one page is enough. Professors or committee normally have no time to scan a long letter. Make sure your first paragraph is impressive.</p>
</li>
</ol>
